{"tid":1972353,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新加坡新增334宗確診個案","createTime":"2020-04-14T12:46:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T08:42:26.000Z","uid":41404,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"df449d286ab05c11fb2e9e13bfdf02e3e60934a5","tid":1972353,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:46:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/health/coronavirus-334-new-coronavirus-cases-bringing-total-to-3252\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.straitstimes.com%2Fsingapore%2Fhealth%2Fcoronavirus-334-new-coronavirus-cases-bringing-total-to-3252&d=toob0nj6ijAdanGp0CPeWfkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=d718e88c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/health/coronavirus-334-new-coronavirus-cases-bringing-total-to-3252</a>"},{"pid":"58659f2ac86f30f30e9d476c19f0d5e1683e2c94","tid":1972353,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:46:21.000Z","msg":"SINGAPORE - Singapore reported 334 new coronavirus cases on Tuesday (April 14), bringing the total number of cases to 3,252 since the start of the outbreak.<br />\n<br />\nOf the new cases, 189 are linked to known clusters, 23 are linked to other local cases, and 122 are as yet unlinked.<br />\n<br />\nNone was imported, said the Health Ministry's director of medical services, Associate Professor Kenneth Mak, at a press conference on Tuesday (April 14).<br />\n<br />\nCommenting on the unlinked cases, Prof Mak said they did not necessarily mean that there is an unknown source of transmission and, as a result, community spread.<br />\n<br />\nSome of the numbers are from active testing done in different settings - not just in larger purpose-built dormitories, but also other smaller ones, and it takes time to compile and match the figures, he said.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;So, in fact, out of the proportion that are as yet unlinked, you will find that over the next few days that number whittles down progressively as we link them to existing clusters,&quot; he added.<br />\n<br />\nGiving an update on the work of an inter-agency task force a week after it was set up to support foreign workers, the Manpower Ministry Permanent Secretary Aubeck Kam said the teams deployed to all 43 purpose-built dormitories since last week have stabilised living conditions there.<br />\n<br />\nMr Kam said the next phase of operations, which is &quot;very critical&quot;, would involve putting in place medical support so workers can receive good treatment.<br />\n<br />\nThe task force plans to set up medical posts at all 43 dormitories by the middle of this week, said its commander, Chief Guards Officer Seet Uei Lim."},{"pid":"23910940ef3da02c72b98ac8d4bbcc4c53b9d56b","tid":1972353,"uid":4174,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:47:11.000Z","msg":"monkey.... 講到口都臭"},{"pid":"442e4ac666bd651ec06ab40c943a2ac0af2f4f17","tid":1972353,"uid":17397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:48:07.000Z","msg":"monkey cannot see"},{"pid":"5de768b9298cc412692c593e85af8def7c582c28","tid":1972353,"uid":36134,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:48:38.000Z","msg":"呢個數係今日中午12截數<br />\n成件事好撚吊詭<br />\n今日盤數應該好撚大<br />\nKing Monkey先出此下策"},{"pid":"3a093b67274920ea2a01a846f859d99059398f12","tid":1972353,"uid":156913,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:51:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://techliberation.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/Monkey-w-a-gun.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechliberation.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2010%2F05%2FMonkey-w-a-gun.jpg&h=1d1bc787&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2030573193cc091e6e219c9f931b00d3f7853272","tid":1972353,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5de768b9298cc412692c593e85af8def7c582c28","tid":1972353,"uid":36134,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"rep